OL,3,CHundreds marched in protest against US
OL,4,Cand Israeli attacks on Iran
OL,6,FHundreds of people marched through
OL,7,FLondon yesterday afternoon condemning
OL,8,FAmerica and Israel's attacks on Iran.
OL,10,FActivists waved placards on Saturday
OL,11,Fthat read "stop Trump's wars", "tell
OL,12,FStarmer: stop arming Israel", "end
OL,13,Fnuclear hypocrisy" and "stop bombing
OL,14,FIran".
OL,16,FMeanwhile, less than two and a half
OL,17,Fmiles away from the protest's finish
OL,18,Fpoint, fewer than a hundred people
OL,19,Fdemonstrating against the Iranian
OL,20,Fgovernment thanked the US and Israel
OL,21,Ffor getting involved in their country.
