OL,3,CHundreds marched in protest against US
OL,4,Cand Israeli attacks on Iran
OL,6,FStop the War Coalition's march against
OL,7,Fthe conflicts in Israel, Lebanon and
OL,8,FPalestine started in Russell Square,
OL,9,Fcentral London, and ended with
OL,10,Fspeeches outside Downing Street.
OL,12,FThe group said previously: "We demand
OL,13,Fnothing short of a complete break from
OL,14,FTrump and his criminal foreign policy."
OL,16,FIt was part of the "Stop Bombing Iran
OL,17,FDay Of Action" which also saw events
OL,18,Fin Manchester, west Cornwall,
OL,19,FBirmingham and Cardiff.
OL,26,@tD@\OUvD@gO]xD@TOUyD@NO]
