OL,3,CHundreds marched in protest against US
OL,4,Cand Israeli attacks on Iran
OL,6,FProtesters followed large Stop the War
OL,7,FCoalition, Campaign for Nuclear
OL,8,FDisarmament and Palestine Solidarity
OL,9,FCampaign banners.
OL,11,FAddressing the crowd in Whitehall,
OL,12,FShabbir Lakha, from Stop the War
OL,13,FCoalition, said people in Iran,
OL,14,FPalestine and Lebanon are marking Eid
OL,15,F"under the hail of American and
OL,16,FIsraeli bombs next to the rubble of
OL,17,Ftheir homes and the graves of their
OL,18,Floved ones".
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@KO]
