OL,6,FHe added: "Let us be done with
OL,7,FStarmer's lies that Britain is not
OL,8,Finvolved in this war."
OL,10,FLater outside the Iranian embassy in
OL,11,FKensington, west London, Stage for
OL,12,FFreedom protesters chanted beside a
OL,13,Flarge sign that said: "Thank you, Mr
OL,14,FPresident Donald John Trump. Thank
OL,15,Fyou, Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,16,FNetanyahu."
