OL,3,CHundreds marched in protest against US
OL,4,Cand Israeli attacks on Iran
OL,6,FThe banner criticised the Islamic
OL,7,FRevolutionary Guard Corps "and its
OL,8,Ftyrant leadership" which has "left
OL,9,Fprofound wounds on many families" in
OL,10,Fthe 47 years since the Islamic
OL,11,FRevolution.
OL,13,FIt said: "Iranians are deeply
OL,14,Fheartbroken by the loss of American
OL,15,Fsoldiers' lives and those who were
OL,16,Fkilled in Israel.
OL,18,F"We send our love and prayers for
OL,19,Fthose who stood against oppression and
OL,20,Fgave their precious lives in the hope
OL,21,Fof a safer, freer world."
