OL,6,FOther placards claimed the only
OL,7,Flegitimate head of Iran's transitional
OL,8,Fgovernment would be Reza Pahlavi, the
OL,9,Fexiled son of Iran's last shah, who
OL,10,Fwas overthrown during the 1979 Islamic
OL,11,FRevolution.
OL,13,FDemonstrators waved Iranian, American
OL,14,Fand Israeli flags and shouted "UK
OL,15,FGovernment, shame on you, shame on
OL,16,Fyou", "Israel, USA, thank you, thank
OL,17,Fyou", and "shut the Islamic terrorist
OL,18,Fembassy".
